TravelApp 🌍
A simple, fast, and interactive travel planner to explore destinations and find suggested tours.

TravelApp lets you quickly choose a destination and instantly view hand-picked tour suggestions. Just click Start, select a place you'd like to visit, and discover curated travel ideas—no sign-up, no clutter.

✨ Features
🎯 Pick a Destination
Choose where you want to go with a single click.

🗺️ Instant Tour Suggestions
Browse curated tours and activities based on your selected location.

⚡ Lightweight & Fast
Built with pure HTML, CSS, and JavaScript—no frameworks or dependencies.

🚀 Getting Started
To run the app locally:

```
bash 
git clone https://github.com/snikmas/TripApp
cd TripApp
npm install
```

